  "comment": "Pro Lux LUX LED 740: A complete kit of 2 MHL740 moving heads supplied in a solid and rugged flightcase. The MHL740 is a wash moving head with a linear motorized zoom equipped with 7 ultra-bright 40 Watt 4-in-1 LEDs according to the latest technology. This moving head is setup with extremely powerful noise-reducing motors, enabling ultra-fast pan and tilt movement while keeping the noise to a bare minimum. Perfectly useable for many events and club installs.\n\n7x 40W 4-in-1 RGBW LED",
